CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,FA Greater Manchester Police Officer
OL,7,Fwho crashed into a woman's car during
OL,8,Fa high speed pursuit has been giving
OL,9,Fevidence in the trial against him.
OL,11,FMark Burrows, 46 from Reddish,
OL,12,FStockport, pleaded not guilty to
OL,13,Fcausing the death of Heather Smedley,
OL,14,F53, by dangerous driving and not
OL,15,Fguilty to a second charge of causing
OL,16,Fher death by careless driving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
