OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,FThe jury watched dash cam video that
OL,7,Fshowed PC Burrows reached speeds of
OL,8,Fmore 80 mph as he pursued a stolen car
OL,9,Fthrough Oldham. He said he was
OL,10,F"satisfied that the speed was
OL,11,Fappropriate"
OL,13,FThe Police Officer had been made aware
OL,14,Fof three stolen vehicles in the area
OL,15,Fand was working with other units to
OL,16,Fapprehend the drivers.
OL,18,FThe fatal collision happened at
OL,19,F10.20am on December 23 2022 on Otmoor
OL,20,FWay in Oldham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,FPC Burrows told the court he has been
OL,7,Fa Police Officer for 25 years and in
OL,8,F2011 became an advanced police driver.
OL,9,FHe is a fully trained member of the
OL,10,FTactical Vehicle Intercept Unit.
OL,12,FHe told the court:
OL,14,F"I was using all my skills and
OL,15,Ftraining to conduct that pursuit,
OL,16,Fconducting it to the best of my
OL,17,Fability"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,FPC Burrows explained that as part of
OL,7,Fthe training he has to make a dynamic
OL,8,Frisk assessment and read the cues from
OL,9,Ffellow drivers and members of the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,FHe was moving to overtake four moving
OL,13,Fvehicles when he said:
OL,15,F"very tragically Mrs Smedley's car
OL,16,Fturned across my path"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,F"At that moment in time I was more
OL,7,Fthan convinced that Mrs Smedley's
OL,8,Fvehicle was yielding to me, otherwise
OL,9,FI would not have attempted the
OL,10,Fovertake."
OL,12,F"When that perception changed I had
OL,13,Fone second to react"
OL,15,FPC Burrows had to stop giving evidence
OL,16,Fto wipe tears from his eyes as he was
OL,17,Fasked about the collision and the
OL,18,Fimmediate aftermath. He said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,F"My memory following the crash is
OL,7,Ffragmented, there are certain things I
OL,8,Fwill never forget and there are
OL,9,Fcertain things I cannot remember"
OL,11,FHe explained that an ambulance was
OL,12,Fcalled and he tried to open the car
OL,13,Fdoor to get to Mrs Smedley
OL,15,F"I tried to communicate with her and
OL,16,Fheld her hand"
OL,18,FPC Burrows was at the wheel of an
OL,19,Funmarked police car but had sirens and
OL,20,Fblue lights on during the pursuit of
OL,21,Fan Audi A3.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
