OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778058353
OL,3,CPolice Officer driving at over 80mph
OL,4,Cbefore fatal collision
OL,6,FThe police car crashed into a Peugeot
OL,7,F108 driven by Mrs Smedley.
OL,9,FShe died at the scene of the crash in
OL,10,FOldham.
OL,12,FAfter her death, Ms Smedley's family
OL,13,Fpaid tribute to "the most kind,
OL,14,Fgentle, beautiful soul inside and out".
OL,26,@uD@QOUvD@fO]
